data.description: 3 bedroom, 3 bath home with bonus room. Only 3 years old! Open & Spacious floor plan with 3 bedrooms and 2 full baths on the main level. Split bedroom plan. Upstairs you will find a huge 17x24 bonus room that has a closet and a full bath. Conveniently located in the Reidville community, between Spartanburg and Greenville. Short drive to Tyger River Park, shopping, dining, etc. Don't miss this opportunity to make this remarkable home yours!
